{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-notifications01",
    "name": "Notifications Service - CiblOrgaSport",
    "description": "Endpoints REST du notifications-service (port 8089). Les notifications sont créées automatiquement via Kafka quand un incident est publié. Le push temps réel se fait en WebSocket STOMP sur ws://localhost:8089/ws → topic /topic/notifications/{spectateurId}.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "notif_base",
      "value": "http://localhost:8089"
    },
    {
      "key": "spectateur_id",
      "value": "1"
    },
    {
      "key": "notification_id",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Historique",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Toutes les notifications d'un spectateur",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test(\"Réponse est un tableau\", () => {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(data).to.be.an('array');",
                  "});",
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (data.length > 0) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('notification_id', data[0].id);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('notification_id', data[0].id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "id": "notif-001",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{notif_base}}/api/notifications/spectateur/{{spectateur_id}}",
              "host": ["{{notif_base}}"],
              "path": ["api", "notifications", "spectateur", "{{spectateur_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Retourne toutes les notifications du spectateur triées par date décroissante."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Notifications non lues",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test(\"Toutes les entrées sont non lues\", () => {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "    data.forEach(n => pm.expect(n.lu).to.equal(false));",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "id": "notif-002",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{notif_base}}/api/notifications/spectateur/{{spectateur_id}}/non-lues",
              "host": ["{{notif_base}}"],
              "path": ["api", "notifications", "spectateur", "{{spectateur_id}}", "non-lues"]
            },
            "description": "Retourne uniquement les notifications avec lu=false."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Compteur non lues (badge)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test(\"Champ nonLues présent\", () => {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(data).to.have.property('nonLues');",
                  "    pm.expect(data.nonLues).to.be.a('number');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "id": "notif-003",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{notif_base}}/api/notifications/spectateur/{{spectateur_id}}/compteur",
              "host": ["{{notif_base}}"],
              "path": ["api", "notifications", "spectateur", "{{spectateur_id}}", "compteur"]
            },
            "description": "Retourne { \"nonLues\": N }. Utile pour afficher un badge dans l'UI."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "id": "notif-folder-historique"
    },
    {
      "name": "Actions",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Marquer une notification comme lue",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test(\"lu=true dans la réponse\", () => {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(data.lu).to.equal(true);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "id": "notif-004",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{notif_base}}/api/notifications/{{notification_id}}/lue",
              "host": ["{{notif_base}}"],
              "path": ["api", "notifications", "{{notification_id}}", "lue"]
            },
            "description": "Marque la notification identifiée par notification_id comme lue (lu=true)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Tout marquer comme lu",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 200\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test(\"Champ mis_a_jour présent\", () => {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(data).to.have.property('mis_a_jour');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "id": "notif-005",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{notif_base}}/api/notifications/spectateur/{{spectateur_id}}/tout-lire",
              "host": ["{{notif_base}}"],
              "path": ["api", "notifications", "spectateur", "{{spectateur_id}}", "tout-lire"]
            },
            "description": "Marque toutes les notifications non lues du spectateur comme lues. Retourne { \"mis_a_jour\": N }."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Supprimer une notification",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status 204\", () => pm.response.to.have.status(204));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "id": "notif-006",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{notif_base}}/api/notifications/{{notification_id}}",
              "host": ["{{notif_base}}"],
              "path": ["api", "notifications", "{{notification_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Supprime définitivement la notification. Retourne 204 No Content."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "id": "notif-folder-actions"
    },
    {
      "name": "WebSocket – Info",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "⚠ WebSocket STOMP (hors Postman)",
          "id": "notif-ws-info",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{notif_base}}/ws/info",
              "host": ["{{notif_base}}"],
              "path": ["ws", "info"]
            },
            "description": "Ce GET vérifie que l'endpoint SockJS répond (retourne un JSON de négociation SockJS).\n\nPour recevoir des notifications en temps réel, utiliser Hoppscotch (hoppscotch.io → Realtime → STOMP) :\n- URL    : ws://localhost:8089/ws/websocket\n- Subscribe : /topic/notifications/{spectateurId}\n\nFormat du message reçu :\n{\n  \"id\": 42,\n  \"type\": \"INCIDENT\",\n  \"contenu\": \"Nouvel incident (TECHNIQUE) à Tribune A: Incident test\",\n  \"dateEnvoi\": \"2026-02-27T10:00:00\",\n  \"idEvent\": 1001,\n  \"idSpectateur\": 1,\n  \"sourceEventId\": \"evt-abc-123\",\n  \"lu\": false\n}"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "id": "notif-folder-ws"
    }
  ]
}
